title: The Love Story of Elizabeth Taylor and Richard Burton: Hollywood's Most Iconic Couple

sources.title: The Love Story of Elizabeth Taylor and Richard Burton: Hollywood's Most Iconic Couple
sources.description:
The most talked about couple of the 1960's: Elizabeth Taylor & Richard Burton, made dozens of films together, and even walked down the aisle, and, out the divorce court twice! This is the tale of this legendary couple. 

Director & Writer : Bertrand Tessier

Elizabeth Taylor movies: https://youtu.be/7GGqFReLGXI, https://youtu.be/7GGqFReLGXI

Richard Burton movies: https://youtu.be/kOoN0JrakaI
